name: Fuki Sushi
review: Fuki Sushi is a traditional sushi restaurant located in Palo Alto on the peninsula between San Jose and San Francisco, California.
The fish at Fuki Sushi was excellent!

name: Musashi
review: Musashi is located in Southfield, a suburb of Detroit. Detroit is not the first place one thinks of for sushi, even so Musashi is very good.
